$ PLS-00157: Only schema-level programs allow AUTHID

The `→ development/databases/Oracle/PL-SQL/authid` clause cannot be applied to individual functions or procedures of a
PL/SQL package or type. Trying to do so results in the → development/databases/Oracle/PL-SQL/errors-warnings[PL/SQL error]
*PLS-00157: Only schema-level programs allow AUTHID*.

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/PL-SQL/errors-warnings[PL/SQL warnings and errors]
